  "recipe_type": null,
  "brief_description": "Tuna Sandwich Spread makes any bread tastes better. In my case, it goes best with pandesal and loaf bread (it is also known as tasty bread). This Tuna Spread Recipe is simple and straightforward. I like this tuna sandwich spread version because it is basic. It has this good taste into it that most people will\u2026",
  "cuisine": null,
  "instructions": [
    {
      "position": 1,
      "text": "Arrange the onion in a bowl. Microwave for 30 seconds."
    },
    {
      "position": 2,
      "text": "Add the remaining ingredients in the same bowl."
    },
    {
      "position": 3,
      "text": "Fold the ingredients until well blended."
    },
    {
      "position": 4,
      "text": "Use as a sandwich spread for Pandesal. Enjoy!"
    }
  ],
